<br>
The story is still fairly analogous even at the high end, though the advantage of Enraging Blow procs does favor DW more.<br>
<br>
MoK is supposed to scale toward weapon delay and you end up getting about the same amount of life overtime.  Faster weapons gets less back from MoK type spells otherwise if you look at Mark of Kings (minus DS by 9), using 2 20 delay weapons, assuming you always DW/double and you land exactly 50% of your hits, you land 2 hits every second (max haste of course).  That's 18 HP gained per second, or 108 per tick, which is a pretty outrageous amount of regen just for swinging your weapons. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=468916">Phantron</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kujawa>Kujawa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/03 5:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4916.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ??</span><hr size=1> From these posts is it safe to say, my windblade will out-damage and out-taunt a fleshgrinder w/ Longsword of freedom combo? Just hit 56 so the windblade is 50/44. Thanks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=scargoth>Scargoth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/26/03 11:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4916.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ??</span><hr size=1> I'm not quite sold on the 2h weapons myself since the ones I have used cannot hold agro better than my 1h combos right now.  My best 2h weapon right now is a Reaver (40/40) which gives me between 10 and 15 DPS LESS than my 1h combo of CHSD (13/19) and FG (12/19).  I have not yet tried a windblade since I can't afford one yet, but I have a hard time seeing how I would be doing enough dmg with one to beat out my 1h weapons since the ratio isn't that much better than the Reaver.<br>
